spec.description:
Used to visualise metrics collected from the mikenye/readsb-protobuf docker image.

Currently without the polar range and tracked aircraft sections. Also missing MLAT metrics from the prometheus exporter for the time being

targets.query: SELECT last("Lat") FROM "aircraft" WHERE ("host" = 'readsb' AND "Icao" != '') AND time >= now() - 1m GROUP BY "Icao"
SELECT last("Lat"), "Long", "Alt", "Spd" FROM "aircraft" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$hostname$/ AND "Call" != '') AND time >= now() - 1m GROUP BY "Icao", "Call"

spec.title: Readsb-protobuf
